                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <p class="text-success font-medium"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-1"></i>Priority 1: CloudWatch</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">ECS, Lambda, and more</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <p class="text-warning font-medium"><i class="fas fa-file mr-1"></i>Priority 2: Documents</p>
