                            <div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium"><i class="fas fa-comment mr-1"></i>Priority 3: Friendly Message</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Helpful guidance for developers</p>
